Subcommands:
  init         Scaffold repos.yaml, policies/, logs/, .env.example,
               docs/env-setup.md, and .claude/{agents,commands}/ for the
               three bundled sub-agents and slash commands
  repos        List or modify configured repos
    repos list  List entries (default action)
    repos add   Register a new repo (`grava init` + install canonical
                grava agents/skills into <path>/.claude/)
